headline: Aramis Announces New Fragrance, Intuition, with Dwyane Wade as Global Ambassador
summary: NEW YORK, May 06, 2025--Today, Aramis announces the launch of Intuition by Aramis, marking a new chapter for the legendary men’s fragrance brand. Dwyane Wade will serve as Global Ambassador and the face of Intuition by Aramis, launching in August 2025, having collaborated closely with the brand on the campaign storytelling and creative expression.
